<br>
Everyone else was doing celebrities and sports people but I swear I couldn't think of anyone. There were plenty of celebrities I liked, sure, but I didn't think they deserved hero status.<br>
In the end I choose my sister. I don't know, she looked out for me. The teacher actually wasn't impressed, but then she never liked me anyway.<br>
